{"tid":1815867,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"若本港爆發武漢肺炎　係買股買樓時機？","createTime":"2020-01-08T00:00:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T00:01:51.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"58b1fea2af24a10c2697799925467438c3428d3d","tid":1815867,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T00:00:10.000Z","msg":"美伊緊張局勢同埋武漢爆發不明原因肺炎，都令金融市場憂慮黑天鵝再現。同我哋比較近身嘅武漢肺炎疫情，唔少人都會諗返起2003年沙士，當年本港股市樓市都陷入低谷，但其實對市場嘅影響只係好短暫。<br />\n<br />\n睇返當年嘅數據，2月21日病毒傳入香港，當日恒指收報9250點，約兩個月後見全年低位8409點，跌咗9%，之後疫情受控，6月初指數就重上10000點，年底更升至12575點。<br />\n<br />\n至於樓市方面，中原城市領先指數喺病毒傳入起計，到同年8月見底，跌咗10.5%，之後好快就反彈，依家比起當時更加累升咗約4倍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=375844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D375844&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TUBSGL744lGwoqCHTcH8MN0%3D&h=fe8279f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D375844&h=0cc7879f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=375844</a>"},{"pid":"cdcfaf695714d593bdb6f8a3f7a6e220515f42da","tid":1815867,"uid":133727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T00:01:51.000Z","msg":"係"}]}